RUNNING YANFOE
--------------
YANFOE 2.0 does NOT require installation. 

You are, however, required to install .NET Framework 4.0
http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/details.aspx?FamilyID=9cfb2d51-5ff4-4491-b0e5-b386f32c0992&displaylang=en

To start YANFOE 2.0 double click "YANFOE.exe"

BUILDING YANFOE
---------------
YANFOE 2.0 is written in C# 4.0.

The source code for YANFOE can be obtained from the YANFOE code repository.
https://github.com/yanfoe/YANFOE.v2

To build your own copy of YANFOE you will need to install and acquire licenses for the following products:

+ Visual Studio 2010 (http://www.microsoft.com/visualstudio/en-gb)
+ DevExpress WinForms Controls (http://www.devexpress.com/Products/NET/Controls/WinForms/)

